---
import DocLayout from "../layouts/DocLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
---

<DocLayout title="Changelog">
  <PageHero
    slot="hero"
    eyebrow="History"
    title="Changelog"
    icon="lucide:history"
    lede="High-level summary of releases. The canonical, authoritative changelog lives in CHANGELOG.md in the repository."
  />
  <p>
    See <a
      href="https://github.com/IEvangelist/resource-translator/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md"
      rel="noopener"
      target="_blank">CHANGELOG.md</a
    > for the full record.
  </p>

  <h2>v3 (in development)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Bumped to <code>node24</code> runtime (BREAKING).</li>
    <li>
      New inputs: <code>include</code>, <code>exclude</code>, <code
        >configPath</code
      >, <code>categoryId</code>, <code>apiVersion</code>, <code>dryRun</code>,
      <code>failOnError</code>, plus advanced Translator knobs <code
        >textType</code
      >, <code>profanityAction</code>, <code>profanityMarker</code>, and <code
        >allowFallback</code
      >.
    </li>
    <li>
      Source locale is now also forwarded to Translator as <code
        >from=&lt;locale&gt;</code
      > so short strings aren't autodetected.
    </li>
    <li>Repo-level config via <code>.github/resource-translator.yml</code>.</li>
    <li>Glossary support, step summary via <code>core.summary</code>.</li>
    <li>esbuild bundler, ESLint 9 flat config, Prettier, EditorConfig.</li>
    <li>npm audit clean (0 vulnerabilities).</li>
    <li>Astro + Tailwind v4 docs site with view transitions and Expressive Code.</li>
    <li>Dependabot auto-merge, CodeQL scanning, CI matrix.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>v2.x</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>See git history.</li>
  </ul>
</DocLayout>

